fb","tid":600413,"uid":55924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"希望佢堅強<br />\n唔好好似之前幾優中大女生身殘心不殘 結果搵唔到工自殺死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4e98b89c987df19d4b72a13254be09cbae69d4","tid":600413,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望佢堅強<br />\n唔好好似之前幾優中大女生身殘心不殘 結果搵唔到工自殺死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果政府捧佢咪得囉，卡碧都係咁上位啫，順風順水"},{"pid":"ebe44ddf645049d9b76e68275f69bf020d9a4fca","tid":600413,"uid":171835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e4e98b89c987df19d4b72a13254be09cbae69d4","tid":600413,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望佢堅強<br />\n唔好好似之前幾優中大女生身殘心不殘 結果搵唔到工自殺死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果政府捧佢咪得囉，卡碧都係咁上位啫，順風順水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6431598c028a847d7d15f612bc228e3e4bd32af6","tid":600413,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"現代海倫凱勒"},{"pid":"2db130fb70c102dfbfd711fc21d57a7dd0b96193","tid":600413,"uid":46231,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b22300d38ba1deba0713161aab9b3dbff0d4e94b","tid":600413,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"又話盲又讀唇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"真&middot;盲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95786a1f65e733f7b4e2f852170a64b2f581b507","tid":600413,"uid":171835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj